    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Welcome to the Drift Valley! Get on with the local car culture. Start your journey by buying your first car, practice your driving skills and upgrade your ride.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Upgrade and tune your car!</h2>Increase the power of your engine and change its parameters, fine-tune the suspension and don't forget about the external styling of the car.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2390290/extras/019a8fc1d9074fd2ccd22e16b1b4cdbd.poster.avif?t=1752758188\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2390290/extras/019a8fc1d9074fd2ccd22e16b1b4cdbd.webm?t=1752758188\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2390290/extras/019a8fc1d9074fd2ccd22e16b1b4cdbd.mp4?t=1752758188\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Explore the open world of drift valley!</h2>Urban areas and mountain passes, narrow city streets and wide highways with multi-level interchanges, gas stations and roadside shops, workshops are waiting for you in the drift valley!<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2390290/extras/83d86d6698c1cc79abff50c96ecea2d8.poster.avif?t=1752758188\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2390290/extras/83d86d6698c1cc79abff50c96ecea2d8.webm?t=1752758188\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2390290/extras/83d86d6698c1cc79abff50c96ecea2d8.mp4?t=1752758188\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Drive with pleasure</h2>All cars are different and have their own character, but it's a pleasure to drive each one!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2390290/extras/71b3b8631041f2ca1d359a3aded2deb0.poster.avif?t=1752758188\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2390290/extras/71b3b8631041f2ca1d359a3aded2deb0.webm?t=1752758188\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2390290/extras/71b3b8631041f2ca1d359a3aded2deb0.mp4?t=1752758188\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul>",
